  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Twin Rooms</strong> are around 19m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a shower and some rooms have a balcony, which can be requested at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms</strong> are around 24m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a balcony and a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are around 35m² and sleep up to four people (extra beds are two single sofa beds). They have a bath with an overhead shower and a walk-in wardrobe. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Twin Rooms for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
